  "description": {
    "canonical": "A gobbet of raw flesh, fallen from the wyrm Vome in her death spasm. Used to attract Chondricord and Duriod in Cambion Drift cave hotspots during Fass and Vome.\n\nLocation: Cambion Drift on Deimos while Fass is active",
    "display": "在蛟龙“秩序”的死亡痉挛时，从她身上掉下来的一块生肉。可以用来吸引“秩序”/“混乱”期间魔胎之境洞穴鱼点中的骨锥琼鲷和韧铠灵鲷。\n\n获取地点：“混乱”活跃时的火卫二魔胎之境"
  },
